**Priority:** Normal

**Severity:** Minor

**Reproducibility:** Always

**Platform:** Google Chrome 63.0.3239.132

**OS:** Windows

**OS Version:** 7 x86

**Summary:** The borders of the text box are extended beyond the border of the "Contact us" page after changing the size of the text box

**Description:** The borders of the text box are extended beyond the border of the "Contact us" page after changing the size of the text box

**Steps To Reproduce:**

1. Go to the site http://prestashop******
2. Open the page "Contact us" on the top right corner
3. Pull the corner of the text input window to the right and down
4. Pay attention to the borders of the text box

**Actual result:** The borders of the text box are extended beyond the border of the "Contact us" page after changing the size of the text box

**Expected result:** The borders of the text box are not extended beyond the border of the "Contact us" page after changing the size of the text box

**Additional Information:**

**Environment:**

*Mozilla Firefox 52.4.0*

*IE 11.0*

*Chrome 63.0.3239.132*

